<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>로그인 - 매체 raw 허브</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-box card">
    <h1>매체 raw 허브</h1>
    <form method="POST" action="/login">
      <label>이메일</label>
      <input type="email" name="email" autofocus style="width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;">
      <label>비밀번호</label>
      <input type="password" name="password" style="width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;">
      <button type="submit" style="width:100%;">로그인</button>
    </form>
    <% if (error) { %><div class="error"><%= error %></div><% } %>
    <div class="hint" style="margin-top:14px;">
      계정이 없으신가요? <a href="/signup">회원가입 (@<%= allowedDomain %> 이메일만 가능)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
